OL,3,CFunding announced for safety works at
OL,4,Cmore than 130 coal tip sites across
OL,5,CWales
OL,7,FAlmost #34 million has been promised
OL,8,Fby the Welsh Government to deliver
OL,9,Fsafety works at 130 coal tip sites
OL,10,Fthroughout Wales.
OL,12,FThe funding was confirmed by the
OL,13,FDeputy First Minister Huw Irranca-
OL,14,FDavies and Cabinet Secretary for
OL,15,FFinance Mark Drakeford, on a visit to
OL,16,FDyffryn Rhondda Colliery in the Afan
OL,17,FValley on Wednesday (19th March).
