OL,7,FHe said: "When combined with the #25
OL,8,Fmillion investment from the UK
OL,9,FGovernment announced in the Autumn
OL,10,FBudget, we will have dedicated over
OL,11,F#100 million to coal tip safety during
OL,12,Fthis Senedd term ` demonstrating our
OL,13,Fcommitment to protecting communities
OL,14,Fand addressing this crucial
OL,15,Finfrastructure challenge."
OL,17,FHuw Irranca-Davies added after
OL,18,Fvisiting residents who live near these
OL,19,Fsites and hearing their concerns, he
OL,20,Fwas proud to deliver credible safety
OL,21,Fimprovements for these communities.
