OL,7,FConcerns over coal tip safety were
OL,8,Fraised again last November, after
OL,9,Fheavy rainfall during Storm Bert
OL,10,Fcaused a landslide in Cwmtillery,
OL,11,FBlaenau Gwent.
OL,13,FResidents were forced to leave their
OL,14,Fhomes and stay in the nearby leisure
OL,15,Fcentre. The council confirmed the tip
OL,16,Fwas Category D, which has the most
OL,17,Fpotential impact to public safety.
