OL,7,FThis incident emphasised the continued
OL,8,Fimportance of coal tip safety, a
OL,9,Fcritical issue in Wales since the
OL,10,FAberfan disaster of 1966, where a coal
OL,11,Ftip collapse claimed the lives of 116
OL,12,Fchildren and 28 adults at Pantglas
OL,13,FJunior School.
OL,15,FThe Rhondda Cynon Taf Council is set
OL,16,Fthe receive the biggest payment for
OL,17,Ftip safety, at just over #11 million.
OL,19,FThere are 2,573 coal tips in Wales.
